Package de.gianfelice.aeskulab.data.entities

Contains all entities for strategic use of this application.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
EventEntity An entity to store the events, that will be managed by this application.
EventGroup A simple entity to group EventEntity objects.
Helper An entity to manage helpers, that can optionally be linked to a User object.
HelperType A helper "draft" that should be used in squad "drafts".
Log Contains information about events, that happened in the past.
Place Remarkable places, e.g. treatment tent.
Qualification Represents qualifications for each helper.
Squad An entity to group Helper objects inside a squad.
SquadType A squad "draft".
Vehicle An entity to store vehicles.
Work An entity to collect all information about work.
